  "doc_id": "4987",
  "text": "Transport parameters were analyzed using kymograph analysis in the MetaMorph software package (Molecular Devices, Inc.) as previously described [CITATION_1] . Kymographs containing 10 or more traces were analyzed and each were averaged within individual embryos for statistical analysis. The number of particles moving in each direction was estimated based on traces on the kymographs and then normalized to length of axonal segment and total imaging time.",
